sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant Lambda
    participant Bedrock
    participant DDB as DynamoDB
    
    Client->>API: POST /infer {prompt}
    API->>Lambda: Invoke
    Lambda->>Bedrock: InvokeModel(prompt)
    Bedrock-->>Lambda: Response(text)
    Lambda->>DDB: PutItem(result)
    Lambda-->>API: 200 OK {text}
    API-->>Client: 200 OK {text}
